{"data":[{"date":"07:12 22/07","title":"S\u1ed1c: Arsenal l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb Bundesliga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/soc-arsenal-lai-muon-mua-them-mot-thu-mon-nua-tu-bundesliga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer c\u1ee7a Monchengladbach, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb Bundesliga sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cech v\u00e0 Ospina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190220.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua Bernd Leno</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea3 David Ospina v\u00e0 Petr Cech l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, c\u1ea3 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer thay Petr Cech h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer thay Petr Cech h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Arsenal-muon-mua-Yann-Sommer-thay-Petr-Cech-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Petr Cech v\u00e0 Ospina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDavid Ospina \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 quan t\u00e2m, anh \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. Ph\u00eda Arsenal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia ra \u0111i, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPetr Cech hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m. The Blues \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t Courtois v\u00e0o tay Real Madrid, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1982 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Ngo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Napoli c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Cech.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 David Ospina v\u00e0 Petr Cech \u0111\u1ec1u ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Arsenal bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Bernd Leno.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Yann Sommer</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer c\u1ee7a Monchengladbach, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb Bundesliga sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer thay Petr Cech h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer thay Petr Cech h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/soc-arsenal-lai-muon-mua-them-mot-thu-mon-nua-tu-bundesliga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Yann Sommer</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nYann Sommer \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Bundesliga cho CLB Monchengladbach, t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 anh g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9. HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Yann Sommer \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Monchengladbach sau 4 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Arsenal \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Monchengladbach y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Leno, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1498","checkdouble":"191764"},{"date":"07:19 22/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 22/07: MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2207-mu-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-sao-khung-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 22/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 2207 MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 2207 MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 Perisic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2207-MU-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-Perisic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nIvan Perisic s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV c\u1ee7a Inter, Luciano Spalletti.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus t\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 t\u1eeb 44 l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nGonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus t\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 t\u1eeb 44 l\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Giroud</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Italia, Gianluca Di Marzio Atletico Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ander Herrera mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrera v\u1edbi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2019, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Welbeck l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Welbeck CSKA 2-2 Arsenal\" title=\"Welbeck CSKA 2-2 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/CSKA-2-2-Arsenal-Khi-Arsene-Wenger-nghi-qua-nhieu-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Welbeck v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ray Parlor kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-15-trieu-bang-welbeck-la-mon-hoi-voi-moi-doi-bong-172-191759.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/voi-15-trieu-bang-welbeck-la-mon-hoi-voi-moi-doi-bong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-15-trieu-bang-welbeck-la-mon-hoi-voi-moi-doi-bong-172-191759.html\">V\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Welbeck l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</span><br>\r\nDanny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ray Parlor kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Magui l\u00ean 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Digne&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca ban Digne cho Juventus o He 2018\" title=\"Barca b\u00e1n Digne cho Juventus \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Barca-ban-Lucas-Digne-cho-Everton-voi-gia-16-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Digne s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, Everton ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Lucas Digne c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Bayern Munich c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Karim Benzema s\u1eafp t\u1edbi AC Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sky Sport, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1497","checkdouble":"191766"},{"date":"08:35 22/07","title":"Pereira: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho MU\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/pereira-toi-da-san-sang-da-chinh-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andreas Pereira quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man United m\u00f9a n\u00e0y sau khi \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Valencia theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</h2><h2>Pereira quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pereira \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Mestalla trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Anh ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-that-vong-voi-quyet-dinh-ra-di-cua-pereira-172-167901.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Pereira</span> v\u00ec quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man United v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t. V\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ho\u00e0i nghi r\u1eb1ng li\u1ec7u sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pereira mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pereira mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/pereira-toi-da-san-sang-da-chinh-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Andreas Pereira mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Pereira cho r\u1eb1ng qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. V\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Premier League kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng sau.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t \u1edf Valencia v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cQu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Pereira chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf MU</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pereira kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Man United. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Michael Carrick, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau 12 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cHLV \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i n\u00f3i t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 6. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. HLV lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i cho t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCarrick c\u0169ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00f4i trong m\u1ecdi bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 h\u1ecd m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c HLV kh\u00e1c trong \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCarrick l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man United. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0a ra cho t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng m\u1eb9o nh\u1ecf, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u00f4i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. B\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u kh\u00e1 nhanh v\u00e0 th\u1eadt d\u1ec5 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb anh \u1ea5y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-trung-ve-nguoi-anh-len-65-trieu-bang-172-191763.html\">MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00ean 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong-172-191761.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1496","checkdouble":"191767"},{"date":"08:54 22/07","title":"M\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, Herrera v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 \u1edf MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/mat-vi-tri-herrera-van-quyet-tam-bam-tru-o-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrera kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i.</h2><h2>Herrera mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o 12 th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 5 c\u00f9ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-cong-bo-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-nam-khong-phai-ibrahimovic-172-160221.html\" target=\"_blank\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t MU m\u00f9a 2016/17</span> \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 161 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Herrera quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Herrera quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/mat-vi-tri-herrera-van-quyet-tam-bam-tru-o-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Herrera quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHerrera hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Man United nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa d\u00f9 \u0111ang v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi San Jose Earthquakes, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 chia s\u1ebb:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t y\u00eau qu\u00fd c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. V\u1eady n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i bao gi\u1edd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i th\u00edch nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang l\u00e0m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i y\u00eau n\u01a1i n\u00e0y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a MU n\u0103m t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Herrera \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Man United gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup, League Cup v\u00e0 Europa League trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Anh. V\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c trong n\u0103m m\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch hay West Brom tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eadt s\u1ef1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eadp trung trong nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng thi tho\u1ea3ng v\u1eabn m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pereira-toi-da-san-sang-da-chinh-cho-mu-172-191767.html\">Pereira: T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2207-mu-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-sao-khung-croatia-184-191766.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 22/07: MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1495","checkdouble":"191770"},{"date":"22:32 21/07","title":"Li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/lien-tiep-toa-sang-tien-linh-van-chua-nghi-toi-cuoc-chay-dua-voi-tien-linh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i V-Leauge</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 21/7, t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n G\u00f2 \u0110\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u00e0n so g\u0103ng gi\u1eefa hai ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Ti\u1ebfn Linh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1997 v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t V-League 2018 cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ASIAD. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 tin khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ec1u nay, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 11. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Oseni c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3 b\u00e0n. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, d\u00f9 \u2018t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\u2019 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ea3 Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n mang theo tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1494","checkdouble":"191754"},{"date":"22:40 21/07","title":"C\u0110V Anh x\u0103m h\u00ecnh Southgate sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/cdv-anh-xam-hinh-southgate-sau-chien-tich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh x\u0103m h\u00ecnh Gareth Southgate v\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br />\r\nH\u00ecnh x\u0103m si\u00eau x\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1eb9p</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 x\u0103m g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia l\u00ean c\u00e1nh tay c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i n\u1ebfu h\u00ecnh x\u0103m n\u00e0y&hellip; c\u1ef1c x\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi n\u00f3 d\u1ef1a theo h\u00ecnh v\u1ebd c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu con trai 6 tu\u1ed5i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V c\u00f3 t\u00ean Jeff Holt \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd x\u0103m h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0u d\u1ea5u chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0, m\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 quy\u00ean g\u00f3p ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb thi\u1ec7n cho m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n nh\u1ecf trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng Flax Bourton \u1edf Bristol \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ebd ch\u00e2n dung c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Anh, v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 2000 b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n t\u1eadp tranh n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau World Cup, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh x\u0103m h\u00ecnh Gareth Southgate l\u00ean tay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau World Cup, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh x\u0103m h\u00ecnh Gareth Southgate l\u00ean tay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Sau-World-Cup,-mot-CDV-Anh-xam-hinh-Gareth-Southgate-len-tay-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V Anh x\u0103m h\u00ecnh Gareth Southgate tr\u00ean tay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh x\u0103m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Jeff Holt cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh x\u0103m b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Twitter v\u1ec1 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng x\u0103m Gareth Southgate l\u00ean c\u00e1nh tay. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u00f4i x\u0103m phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e1ng y\u00eau n\u00e0y, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ebd b\u1edfi c\u1eadu con trai th\u1ee9 2.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Oscar, \u0111\u1ee9a con trai c\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb9p l\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ee3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sau khi t\u00f4i gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho c\u00f4 \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 n\u00f3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng l\u1edbn cho t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u1eb9p, m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; C\u0110V n\u00e0y k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh C\u0110V Anh x\u0103m h\u00ecnh Gareth Southgate d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y<br />\r\n</strong> <br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u0110V Anh x\u0103m h\u00ecnh Gareth Southgate \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/4.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00ecnh v\u1ebd c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu nh\u00f3c 6 tu\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u0110V Anh x\u0103m h\u00ecnh Gareth Southgate \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Sau World Cup, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh x\u0103m h\u00ecnh Gareth Southgate l\u00ean tay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh l\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 x\u0103m l\u00ean c\u00e1nh tay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u0110V Anh x\u0103m h\u00ecnh Gareth Southgate \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-thu-mon-croatia-tiep-tuc-cuu-thua-dong-doi-khoi-nga-sap-mat-421-191592.html\">Video: Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Croatia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c &ldquo;c\u1ee9u thua&rdquo; \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u1ecfi ng\u00e3 s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ngap-tran-anh-che-ve-man-an-mung-an-tuong-cua-tong-thong-phap-421-191507.html\">Ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\">Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nong-tien-ve-pogba-hat-its-coming-home-che-nhao-nuoc-anh-421-191310.html\">N\u00d3NG: Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba h\u00e1t It's coming home ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, fan cu\u1ed3ng&hellip; nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus xu\u1ed1ng \u0103n m\u1eebng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1493","checkdouble":"191755"},{"date":"06:30 22/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a SLNA tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohamed Salah sang M\u1ef9 c\u00f9ng Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/bi-ramos-ha-do-van-salah-mat-luon-world-cup-184-187111.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mohamed Salah d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> n\u1eb7ng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 v\u1edbi Real Madrid, vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn The Kop thua 1-3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/100-nhm-liverpool-deu-muon-nghe-tin-nay-tu-klopp.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah sang M\u1ef9 c\u00f9ng Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm, Salah \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch 29 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Salah. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Klopp b\u00e1o tin vui t\u1eeb Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah Klopp\" title=\"Salah Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/10/Jamie-Redknapp-Klopp-giup-tien-dao-Mohamed-Salah-toa-sang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp b\u00e1o tin c\u1ef1c vui t\u1eeb Salah</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1edbi \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Salah. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u00e0 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Salah d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf World Cup 2018 song \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Salah tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y ni\u1ec1m vui, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi Salah v\u00e0 Mane sang M\u1ef9 c\u00f9ng Liverpool. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 12 th\u00e1ng 8, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t\".</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1492","checkdouble":"191757"},{"date":"05:23 22/07","title":"Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/20/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Simon Mignolet t\u1edbi Barca l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u1ebfu Jasper Cillessen ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Simon Mignolet t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Simon Mignolet \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Karius. Su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a 2017/18 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c Simon Mignolet t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c Simon Mignolet t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/16/Cuc-soc-Simon-Mignolet-toi-Barca-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Mignolet mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alisson</span> t\u1eeb Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Mignolet l\u00fac n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Sunderland \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Anfield \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Simon Mignolet kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111ang t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cLiverpool b\u1ecf ra g\u1ea7n 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Mignolet bi\u1ebft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i. Liverpool c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mignolet c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Simon Mignolet t\u1edbi Barca l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u1ebfu Jasper Cillessen ra\u00a0\u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mignolet\" title=\"Mignolet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/24/Leicester-2-3-Liverpool-Mot-ke-noi-loan-de-lam-nen-su-khac-biet-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mignolet c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCillessen hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli. N\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan s\u1ebd chi 8 \u0111\u1ebfn\u00a010 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Mignolet. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Alisson v\u00e0 Karius, The Kop s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 cho Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Marc-Andre ter Stegen r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Mignolet c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn c\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nico Vaesen c\u1ee7a Mignolet n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi Barca: \u201cC\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Mignolet s\u1ebd c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1491","checkdouble":"191758"},{"date":"05:37 22/07","title":"\"V\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Welbeck l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/voi-15-trieu-bang-welbeck-la-mon-hoi-voi-moi-doi-bong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ray Parlor kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Welbeck v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Welbeck c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Wenger, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates trong 4 n\u0103m qua l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/HLV-Unai-Emery-muon-Danny-Welbeck-roi-Arsenal-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Danny Welbeck&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 ra s\u00e2n 80 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Arsenal nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi 15 b\u00e0n, anh ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/welbeck-va-ospina-sap-bi-hlv-emery-tong-khoi-arsenal-172-191482.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Arsenal b\u00e1n Welbeck</span> \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. V\u1edbi Lacazette v\u00e0 Aubameyang, c\u1ef1u HLV PSG kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Welbeck.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaily Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1eeb M.U. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Welbeck s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Emery d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Welbeck l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ray Parlor kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Welbeck CSKA 2-2 Arsenal\" title=\"Welbeck CSKA 2-2 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/CSKA-2-2-Arsenal-Khi-Arsene-Wenger-nghi-qua-nhieu-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ray Parlor cho r\u1eb1ng&nbsp;</span>Welbeck l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Welbeck kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, Welbeck ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi kho\u1ea3ng 15 \u0111\u1ebfn 20 b\u00e0n \u1edf NHA n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 28, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb. N\u1ebfu Welbeck \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm. N\u1ebfu chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng, nh\u01b0ng 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng th\u00ec kh\u00e1c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu Arsenal mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Welbeck, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh s\u1ebd h\u1ecfi mua c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. V\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1490","checkdouble":"191759"},{"date":"06:06 22/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Gareth Bale th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool v\u00e0 Man City, Craig Bellamy.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Jose Mourinho quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Gareth Bale M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf Bale t\u1edbi Old Trafford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua Gareth Bale M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf Bale t\u1edbi Old Trafford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Craig Bellamy tin r\u1eb1ng M.U kh\u00f4ng mua\u00a0</span>Bale v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Tuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-gareth-bale-neu-172-191511.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bale s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real Madrid</span> n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Gareth Bale th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool v\u00e0 Man City, Craig Bellamy.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Bale \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. N\u1ebfu M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Bale \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 CLB m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBale kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Bale, song ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cJuventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 mua Ronaldo v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao, song gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, Bale kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bale h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Craig Bellamy tin r\u1eb1ng Gareth Bale s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale Ronaldo\" title=\"Bale Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/8/8/real-madrid-len-ke-hoach-troi-chan-4-sao-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Craig Bellamy kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh\u00a0</span>Bale h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Bernabeu</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Bale. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Ronaldo che ph\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Bale l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi vui nh\u1ea5t khi Ronaldo quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Juventus\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBale \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi Bale s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1489","checkdouble":"191761"},{"date":"06:51 22/07","title":"Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus t\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 t\u1eeb 44 l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u1edbi. Hi\u1ec7n AC Milan quan t\u00e2m Morata, PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Gonzalo Higuain l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bi-mat-dam-phan-mua-higuain-172-191728.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Morata v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Gonzalo Higuain </span>t\u1eeb Juventus. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Napoli, HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Higuain, song d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Juventus kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn The Blues n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus t\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 t\u1eeb 44 l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, Chelsea hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Higuain. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u1edf Italia v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Fali Ramadani, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a Higuain v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea3 Rugani v\u00e0 Pjanic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Gonzalo Higuain, HLV Sarri c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua th\u00eam b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Juventus. Theo \u0111\u00f3 The Blues mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" title=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Cuc-nong-Chelsea-mua-Daniele-Rugani-voi-gia-36-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus nh\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 98 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd d\u00e0ng cho Rugani c\u00f2n 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Pjanic. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 151 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n t\u1edbi 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, bao g\u1ed3m David Luiz, Gary Cahill, Danny Drinkwater, Alvaro Morata v\u00e0 Michy Batshuayi. Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng 165 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1488","checkdouble":"191762"},{"date":"06:24 22/07","title":"MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00ean 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-trung-ve-nguoi-anh-len-65-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho nh\u1eafm Harry Maguire n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Leicester. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-137,-tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-he-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0a Maguire v\u1ec1 MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League 2017/18. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Maguire ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ecf ra l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i \u1edf nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn. Anh ghi 1 b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Maguire \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-50-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-tuyen-anh-172-191089.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Harry Maguire</span>, Mourinho nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Eric Bailly \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Maguire</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Maguire vs Thuy Dien\" title=\"Harry Maguire vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/mu-chot-50-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U chi t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Harry Maguire&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. &ldquo;B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh sau khi \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Mahrez v\u00e0o tay Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, M.U kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Man \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Maguire m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. Mourinho \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Maguire v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Leicester quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Maguire, M.U s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham ho\u1eb7c Leonardo Bonucci c\u1ee7a AC Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1487","checkdouble":"191763"},{"date":"06:42 22/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (22/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2272018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</styl