\u00f9ng Arsenal.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf HLV Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal, HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/HLV-Unai-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Mesut-Ozil-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt \u1edf Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u00ean TTCN, t\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra g\u1ea7n 80 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 5 t\u00e2n binh. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1t s\u1edbm k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm gi\u00fap HLV Emery c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd mang theo nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t cho Arsenal, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEmry \u0111ang si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Arsenal \u0111ang t\u1eadp r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1edbi 8h t\u1ed1i. C\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ef1u HLV PSG \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mesut Ozil h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ozil\" title=\"Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/29/hlv-emery-thiet-chat-ky-luat-ozil-hoi-quan-som-cung-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ozil tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p Mesut Ozil, b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bay t\u1edbi Singapore v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 22/07\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u00e0i Ozil th\u00ec Mohamed Elneny v\u00e0 Alex Iwobi c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Ozil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Arsenal, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1485","checkdouble":"191732"},{"date":"15:23 21/07","title":"Man City th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, Guardiola v\u1eabn h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/HLV-Guardiola.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City m\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Borussia Dortmund trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Pep Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19. H\u1ecd so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Borussia Dortmund t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Soldier Field (Chicago, M\u1ef9) trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Cup Champions.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Kevin De Bruyne, Raheem Sterling, David Silva, Vincent Kompany, Bernardo Silva, Sergio Aguero hay Gabriel Jesus. V\u00ec th\u1ebf t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a The Citizens.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/HLV-Pep-Guardiola-hai-long-voi-cau-thu-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mahrez ra m\u1eaft Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i v\u00e0 uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh Dortmund \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ec9 m\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Algeria kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e1nh n\u1ed5i Man City g\u1ed3m \u0111a ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. H\u1ecd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund b\u1edfi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Mario Gotze.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund, HLV Pep Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City. \u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y song hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d, Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00e0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nhau.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Guardiola\" title=\"HLV Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/HLV-Guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m, s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao \u0111\u1ed9. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a Dortmund. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-tu-tin-soan-ngoi-man-city-172-191690.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool t\u1ef1 tin so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-sterling-172-191666.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rooney-phat-bieu-ve-mu-va-cuoc-dua-vo-dich-172-191513.html\">Rooney tin M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 Man City m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/joe-hart-sang-my-du-dau-cung-man-city-172-191439.html\">Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea9u, Hart \u201cmu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t\u201d sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-bo-cuoc-vu-mateo-kovacic-172-191406.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 Mateo Kovacic</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1484","checkdouble":"191733"}]}